ffects of these drugs and in whom toxicity symptoms may be easily overlooked.', 'Moderate', 'pharmacodynamic', NULL, 'https://ddinter2.scbdd.com/server/interact/87552/', '', 'Oxitriptan, Viloxazine, Vortioxetine, Milnacipran, Tryptophan, Levomilnacipran, Vilazodone', 'Lidocaine, Tetracaine, Ketotifen, Fexofenadine, Loratadine, Desloratadine, Azelastine', 1767369485);
